snippet.title: Friday the 13th: The Game - Dev Diary #1
snippet.description:
Friday the 13th: Dev Diary with IllFonic, LLC. Discussion on upcoming items, new content and what's going on within the development of Friday the 13th: The Game!

Pre-order now on Amazon: 
Xbox - https://goo.gl/zi6fWx
PS4 - https://goo.gl/jbzNJF
